zboard.com/uervdecarreau.showPublicProfile?language=EN>ervdecarreau</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/23/02 10:06:23 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4512.topic>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> dirk of the traitor</span><hr size=1> greetings and salutations to all.<br><br>while waiting for other guildmates to form raid on crystal caverns, another group yelled that there was a nice no drop piercer on a mob they just killed.. and they let me loot it.<br>great delay, great stats EXCEPT.. it has a proc that stuns YOU. lol so it is a cursed weapon..<br><br>i have tried to look this up and have read that it is part of a coldain ring quest (the ninth one i guess). but havent found out anything else, as in what this ninth quest actually is. also have read rumors that there might be a subquest where you can get the curse removed.<br><br>if you could please post anything you know about this weapon it would be greatly appreciated.<br><br>ervdecarreau venommaker<br>36 rogue<br>drinal server <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ulohki.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Lohki</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/23/02 11:29:17 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4512.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: dirk of the traitor</span><hr size=1> It's for the 9th Coldain Ring quest (Coldain Hero's Insignia Ring I think) ..<br><br>You put that in a box Seneschal gives you along with some heads (Murdrick, Peffin, Doldigun, avalanche ale dude, and Juliah) and hit combine .. then you turn that in with your 8th ring and recieve the 9th. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uandrewbb.showPublicProfile?language=EN>AndrewBB</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/23/02 11:52:30 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4512.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: dirk of the traitor</span><hr size=1> No known way to remove a curse from an item. It's tainted with that traitor's bad deeds, so there ya go.<br><br>However as far as I understand it, the proc is True North, so if you can get your tank to face south, it won't impede your backstabbing terribly.<br><br>IIRC the stats are good enough on that thing that it's worth using for a while even with the curse. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uterm00.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Term00</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/anim_1.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/23/02 12:33:14 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4512.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> .</span><hr size=1> When you turn in the box for the 9th ring, you also get back the dirk with the curse removed and improved stats. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uevilmagus.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Evilmagus</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_ball.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/23/02 2:13:05 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4512.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: .</span><hr size=1> The curse is a stun on yourself, when you dothe 9th ring quest the curse gets replaced with a cold based Dd (frostbite?)<br><br>~Evil <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uervdecarreau.showPublicProfile?language=EN>ervdecarreau</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/24/02 12:04:00 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4512.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: .</span><hr size=1> ok stupid question:<br>do you have to do coldain ring quest #1 -8 before doing 9th?<br> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/utakeshimonogatari.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Takeshi Monogatari</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/24/02 12:27:29 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4512.topic&index=6>Reply</a>    <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: dirk of the traitor</span><hr size=1> Yes you need to do the whole chain of quests.<br><br>Furthermore, you need the head from Rodrick for one of the quests, which means in order to do them you'll need to kill Rodrick again.  It also means whoever let you loot it won't be able to progress beyond the 8th ring unless he kills Rodrick again for another dirk. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/utheserpentor.showPublicProfile?language=EN>The Serpentor</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/24/02 3:48:23 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4512.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: dirk of the traitor</span><hr size=1> The weapon has a neat look.  You can get a jagged ice shard, 12/39 or something with sv cold and procs some kinda DD that looks the same from Icewell Keep. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/urobintun.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Robintun</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/26/02 1:15:14 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4512.topic&index=8>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: dirk of the traitor</span><hr size=1> The uncursed version is called the Dirk of the Dain I understand. I can't find the stats for this anywhere, can someone post them pls.<br><br>Robintun<br>52Bard<br> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uprodigious.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Prodigious</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Safehouse Supporter</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/26/02 9:39:04 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4512.topic&index=9>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: dirk of the traitor</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_item_info.html?num=1465">www.magelo.com/eq_item_in...l?num=1465</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--><br><br>sucks, but oh well. check out the ID: &quot;Cleansed dirk of the traitor&quot;<br><br> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/utiiomon.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Tiiomon</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/26/02 11:24:30 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4512.topic&index=10>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: dirk of the traitor</span><hr size=1> It isn't a bad weapon if you are an un-twinked, or new to the game.<br><br>/bonk Prod. Stop thinking uber. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/usielle.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Sielle</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.invalid.net/insomnia/emoticons/silly.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/28/02 3:02:40 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4512.topic&index=11>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: dirk of the traitor</span><hr size=1> Anyone that could honestly finish the 9 rings to get this dirk, wouldn't use it at all.  Don't forget it's no-drop. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uprodigious.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Prodigious</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Safehouse Supporter</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/28/02 6:50:55 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4512.topic&index=12>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: dirk of the traitor</span><hr size=1> hehe yup my thought excactly. and it won't be made droppable because it starts 10th ring (i think, not sure). <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ukobex.showPublicProfile?language=EN>KobeX</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/anim_1.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/28/02 2:54:16 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4512.topic&index=13>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: dirk of the traitor</span><hr size=1> You can get the note to start the 10th ring war by just saying the phrase.  You don't need to hand in the dirk.<br><br>You need the 9th ring to officially start the war anyway (along with the note). <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showPrevMessage?topicID=4512.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showNextMessage?topicID=4512.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4512.topic&index=13><img src=http://www.thesafehouse.org/images/reply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=